OOC: Its nerve gas, use your imagination! Fine, its gas that will take down 
Neurological circuitry. It has the same effect.

    Black Aracnia impatiently waits for Megatron, still watching the vermine 
and the roach make there way through the vents. Little do they know she will 
administer the gas if they try anything.

    Adrax glances around. It was warm inside from the heat off the computers. 
And, the computers could be modified to fit there needs. For now, they just 
needed to know if anyone was going to pay them a visit. Adrax switched on the 
scanners, and then went to inspect the firearms.
